transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hanji.
Executive: Sir, Manish bol raha hu Indiamart.com se. Primrose Multiclass Private Limited se baat kar rahe hain aap?
Customer: Hanji.
Executive: Deepak sahab baat kar rahe hain?
Customer: Hanji.
Executive: Deepak ji, aapne ek request kari thi video meeting ke liye, right? Services ke regarding.
Customer: Nahi, maine nahi ki thi. Dusre number pe aapko call karna padega.
Executive: Okay, sir connect kar rahe hain lekin woh pick nahi kar rahe hain. Toh main ek baar dobara se arrange call kar leta hu, hai na? Woh ek request aayi hui thi. Sir agar ek baar ho toh aap convey kar dijiyega. Team ka ek matlab pichle half an hour se connect karne ki try kar rahe hain lekin baat nahi ho pa rahi hai. Isliye maine aapko. Theek hai, main message deta hu ji unko. Ek baar please dijiyega sir. Thank you sir.
